    "And so, this can clarify why ViT outperformed the SWIN in the conducted experiments.",
    "Maybe the approach of SWIN can increase the computation efficiency of the model; however, this was not so influential in these experiments as the images were not with high resolution, especially with the fact that they represent a cropped part of the original images.",
